subject: Good Day,
body:
Good Day,
I Hope this Mail Finds You Well; Please, I write To Let You Know  If
You Have Received My Previous Message  I Sent You Last Time?
Krystal Hawley From USA
I Await Your Reply.
Warmest Regards,
Krystal Hawley.

subject: Re: Good Day,
body:
Dear Krystal Hawley,

I hope this message finds you well too. I'm afraid I didn't receive any previous messages from you. Could you please resend it or let me know what it was about?

Best wishes,
Odis
